data.description: Beautiful wooded and private setting surrounded by towering White Pines sits this Minnesota Log home.  Located minutes from town and even closer to the Grace Lake public access.  Enjoy the privacy sitting on your large deck and the views out of the oversized windows in the livingroom.  This home features 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, wood floors and ceilings, wood stove, floor heat and a 24 X 30 detached garage.  A new roof was installed on the home 2 years ago.   Set up a private showing and make sure to check out the 360 virtual tour. NOTE: Additional 2.5 acre lot next to this parcel is available for an additional cost, not included with this listing.
